{"tid":146507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩：不應視法官種族為判決對錯理由　　","createTime":"2017-03-07T07:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T07:43:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e560c475cee01ec68e8be50a2c672ae6dc58a99c","tid":146507,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:06:27.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩表示，本港法官有外國國籍在基本法有規定，主要是起草及通過基本法時，外籍法官較多，如果他們不能留任，會對司法制度有影響。<br />\n<br />\n正在北京的梁愛詩說，如現時所有外籍法官都沒資格在香港出任法官，會有好大影響，她認為社會不應以種族，而是能力來決定是否聘用外籍人士作為法官。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩又指，現時華人出任法官的比例已提升，相信日後有關比例會自然地越來越重。<br />\n<br />\n對於有指七警案中法官判刑過重，是由於是外籍法官不懂基本法。梁愛詩認為，如有人不滿可根據制度上訴，法官的種族不應被視為判決對錯的理由，她認為現時基本法及司法機構制度相當好。"},{"pid":"b4ac731536e525686cf83f14394f13805454fe87","tid":146507,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:15:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">現時華人出任法官的比例已提升，相信日後有關比例會自然地越來越重。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f86f389a2e525af3744c51d46381cbb9bd4628","tid":146507,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f835c6e3fb433b7cd57304f60e6aec57fa77d0","tid":146507,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">洋奴梁愛詩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c